<a data-tip="p$t$yu-xiang-8" href="/people/yu-xiang-8">虞翔</a>，<strong title="Too Simple Plan, sometimes Naïve Bayes" class="zu-question-my-bio">Too Simple Plan, sometimes Naïve Ba…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
